<p>Full List includes vocab: <br> Advenio = I arrive <br> Antequam = Before <br> Altus = High / Deep
<br> Bene = Well
<br>Advenio = I arrive
<br>Antequam = Before
<br>Ceteri = The others/ the rest
<br>Colligo = I collect
<br>Coniux = Husband / wife
<br>Capiae = Troops / forces
<br>Constituo = I decide
<br>Cupio  = I want
<br>Effugio = I escape
<br>Erro = I wander / am wrong
<br>EtEt = BothAnd
<br>Discedo = I leave/depart
<br>Do = I give
<br>Duco = I lead
<br>Frusta = In vein
<br>Homo = man
<br>Inter = Between / Among Us
<br>Inquit = He / she / it says
<br>Ingens = Huge
<br>Liberi = Children
<br>Hic = here
<br>Iam = Now, already
<br>Ibi = Here
<br>Itaque = And so
<br>Iterum = Again
<br>Mora = Delay
<br>Mors = Death
<br>Mortuus = Dead


